<tr>
<td><b>Fading Activated Ability Creatures</b>
</td>
<td>Each of this creature with <a href="/Fading" title="Fading">Fading</a> have an activated ability that requires to remove a fade counter from them. White stands out as the only common creature of an otherwise uncommon cycle.
</td>
<td><a class="autocardhref" href="http://www.magiccards.info/query?q=%21Defender+en-Vec" onclick="AutoCard('Defender en-Vec'); return false;" title="Defender en-Vec" style="color: #804000;font-weight: bold;">Defender en-Vec</a>
