<tr>
<td><b>Tribal Recruiters</b>
</td>
<td>Mirroring the Rebel and Mercenary mechanics in white and black, the other colors are given cards which are either Mercenaries or Rebels and have the ability to recruit specific tribe from the library.
</td>
<td>
</td>
<td><a class="autocardhref" href="http://www.magiccards.info/query?q=%21Seahunter" onclick="AutoCard('Seahunter'); return false;" title="Seahunter" style="color: #804000;font-weight: bold;">Seahunter</a> <br /> (<a href="/Merfolks" title="Merfolks" class="mw-redirect">Merfolks</a>)
</td>
<td>
</td>
<td><a class="autocardhref" href="http://www.magiccards.info/query?q=%21Moggcatcher" onclick="AutoCard('Moggcatcher'); return false;" title="Moggcatcher" style="color: #804000;font-weight: bold;">Moggcatcher</a> <br /> (<a href="/Goblins" title="Goblins" class="mw-redirect">Goblins</a>)
