<tr>
<td><b>Parallax Enchantment</b>
</td>
<td>Each of these rare global enchantment has <a href="/Fading" title="Fading">Fading</a> 5, and the ability to exile a ressource from the game until it itself leaves the game. <a class="autocardhref" href="http://www.magiccards.info/query?q=%21Parallax+Wave" onclick="AutoCard('Parallax Wave'); return false;" title="Parallax Wave" style="color: #804000;font-weight: bold;">Parallax Wave</a> is particularly notable for seeing considerable amount of play as a four-of in the Counter-Rebel standard deck of the time.
</td>
<td><a class="autocardhref" href="http://www.magiccards.info/query?q=%21Parallax+Wave" onclick="AutoCard('Parallax Wave'); return false;" title="Parallax Wave" style="color: #804000;font-weight: bold;">Parallax Wave</a> <br /> (creatures)
</td>
<td><a class="autocardhref" href="http://www.magiccards.info/query?q=%21Parallax+Tide" onclick="AutoCard('Parallax Tide'); return false;" title="Parallax Tide" style="color: #804000;font-weight: bold;">Parallax Tide</a> <br /> (lands)
</td>
<td><a class="autocardhref" href="http://www.magiccards.info/query?q=%21Parallax+Nexus" onclick="AutoCard('Parallax Nexus'); return false;" title="Parallax Nexus" style="color: #804000;font-weight: bold;">Parallax Nexus</a> <br /> (cards in hand)
